OL,3,CLong delays as lorry fire closes M5
OL,5,FNational Highways says the load is not
OL,6,Fbelieved to be hazardous, it says it
OL,7,Fis working to reopen lanes as soon as
OL,8,Fit is safe to do so.
OL,10,FUpdates to follow.
